msgid ""
"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Els pagaments en criptomoneda Stripe (USDC) només estan disponibles per a "
"empreses basades als EUA. Si ets fora dels EUA, Stripe només acceptarà "
"pagaments per targeta de crèdit al teu saldo de Stripe (no directament a "
"criptomonedes)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Si estàs als EUA, pots usar Stripe per rebre criptomonedes directament. Si "
"estàs fora, considera NOWPayments o CoinGate per a pagaments directes en "
"criptomonedes."

