msgid "Let My Girl Friend Enjoy Our Coffee"
msgstr "Deixa que la meva companya gaudeixi del nostre cafè"

msgid ""
"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"Un widget poderós i gratuït de donacions i pagaments que permet als teus "
"visitants donar-te suport via targeta de crèdit o criptomoneda (Quai). Sense"
" tarifes mensuals, sense subscripcions de tercers – només el teu moneder i "
"serveis gratuïts."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Alguns navegadors bloquegen scripts de tercers per a la privacitat. Aquest "
"proxy carrega scripts a través del teu propi servidor per evitar aquests "
"bloquejos."

msgid ""
"You can update the script URLs below if the original URLs change or if you "
"want to use a different CDN."
msgstr ""
"Pots actualitzar les URL dels scripts a sota si les URL originals canvien o "
"si vols usar un CDN diferent."

